股的錢多？"},{"pid":"3be63ee2de5c775df306fe812010eb65979fe49d","tid":1954733,"uid":188176,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7d6ec80155ea5c3288555b726c89aa6b6298e28c","tid":1954733,"uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"510353266c035c7fef28cb93e1dc3881fbf7221d","tid":1954733,"uid":188176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9dee398387c5f45568b51af6c6b5bb49bc4bf279","tid":1954733,"uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:58:30.000Z","msg":"自住樓=冇租收<br />\n個仔自住樓供緊=經濟差，交供款都有啲吃力<br />\n<br />\n問：退咗休，平時食股息過活，今年食北風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:04:32.000Z","msg":"人地一年收六十萬又住自己樓<br />\n唔大洗兩年息都夠食十年<br />\n就算得番20蚊都值三百萬食過世<br />\n你同佢擔心？連登仔擔心下自己好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:13:00.000Z","msg":"唔好用窮人支出計有錢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時係季季都有嘅超穩定收入，實大洗（唔少打工仔搵幾多都月月清）<br />\n我估佢平時用開4～5萬一個月，得少少儲蓄<br />\n依家叫佢每月洗少過1萬、再望住股價資產貶值、我怕佢睇唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:27:12.000Z","msg":"「你看，現在的單位1,000萬也買不到，賣掉所有股票也不夠買，而且也不值得買。」<br />\n<br />\n你睇佢講既野就知佢乜人<br />\n佢肯定唔係暴發戶個類<br />\n佢睇佢初期理財就知<br />\n有一大舊錢出黎，窮人會洗左佢<br />\n但佢一半解決住屋基本需要，一半去投資<br />\n成個人生策略好穩陣<br />\n唔好下下用窮人心態去諗人點洗錢<br />\n唔係個個人月入幾多洗幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多時係數字黎"},{"pid":"67423ba6cefb4559b6d37f1a4cbd1224741d69ba","tid":1954733,"uid":186087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:31